<item>
            <title>[JCR-1295] Tablespace (Filegroup) support for MS SQL Server</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/JCR-1295</link>
                <project id="10591" key="JCR">Jackrabbit Content Repository</project>
                        <description>Tablespace support was added for Oracle database servers in this issue&lt;br/&gt;
&lt;br/&gt;
&lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/JCR-968&quot;&gt;https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/JCR-968&lt;/a&gt;&lt;br/&gt;
&lt;br/&gt;
We would like tablespace (or filegroup) support for MS SQL Server as well. To address this, we have created a patch using the trunk of JackRabbit that closely follows the patch in the above named issue.</description>
